quran[98]{c,v,t}:
  19,1,"Kaf, Ha, Ya, Ayn, Swad."
  19,2,"Obwitsulisio bwetsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khumusumba wuwe Zakaria."
  19,3,"Olwa yalanga Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi omulango kwobwifisi."
  19,4,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, toto ebikumba bianje bimalile okhuba ebiteshele, ne omurwe kwanje kwakhanga tsimbutsi, ne shindali weyikhabi imbi tawe Nyasaye wanje Omulesi khulwa okhukhusaba."
  19,5,"Ne toto esie eyendelanga Abandu banje nindakharulaho, ne omukhasi wanje nomukumba. Kho mbelesia witsa okhutong’a mushilenje shianje okhurula khwiwe."
  19,6,"Witsa okhuchelama esie nende okhuchelama olwibulo lwa Yaqub, ne Nyasaye wanje omulesi omukhole omwene abe uchamisia.”"
  19,7,"Ewe Zakaria, toto efwe khukhwetsanga amakhuwa akomwikhoyo ko (okhwibula) omwana, elira lilie ni Yahya, khushili okhuhelesiakhwo yesiyesi imbeli wuwe elira shinga lino."
  19,8,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ndakhanyoola endie omwana omukhasi wanje nali omukumba, nasi ndamala okhukofula muno?”"
  19,9,"Naboola mbu: “Ne endio nilwa kali. Nyasaye wuwo omulesi aboolele mbu: 'Kano ni amangu muno khwisie, ne toto ndakhuloonga khale, ne shiwali eshindu tawe.'"""
  19,10,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje omulesi kholela eshimanyisio.” Naboola mbu: “Eshimanyisio shishio ni mbu sholanyala okhuboola nende abandu khutsinyanga tsitaru tawe nawe nolisa omulamu habwene.”"
  19,11,"Mana narulila abandu baye okhurula mu mihirab, nabasomeselia nomukhono mbu: “Tswenule Nyasaye itsuli nende ingoloobe.”"
  19,12,"Ewe Yahya, tila Eshitabu nende amaani. Nafwe khwamuhelesia oburuchi nashili omutiti."
  19,13,"Ne nikhumuhelesia eshisa okhurula khwifwe nende obutswenufu, ne yali owaria Nyasaye."
  19,14,"Ne (nikhumukhola) omulayi khubebusi bebe, ne shiyali omufuru omukhayi tawe."
  19,15,"Ne omulembe kube khuye inyanga yayebulwa nende inyanga yalifwa, nende inyanga ya alilamusibwa mubafu."
  19,16,"Ne yitsulila Mushitabu Mariam, olwa yawukha khubandu bebe natsia ebuleka webukwe."
  19,17,"Mana naraho eshikalilo okhwiyikalila ehale ninabo. Mana nikhumurumila roho wefu, niyekhola khuye shinga omundu mwene."
  19,18,"(Mariam) Naboola mbu: “Toto esie ndilinda khu Omunji Wetsimbabaasi (yaninde) okhurulana ninawe, toto noba noritsanga Nyasaye."""
  19,19,"(Malaika) Naboola mbu: “Toto esie endi Omurumwa wa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, erumilwe mbu nditse ekhubile akomwikhoyo mbu olanyola omwana omutswenufu.”"
  19,20,"Naboola mbu: “Ndakhanyoola endie omwana ne omundu yesiyesi ashili okhundilakhwo tawe, ne esie kata shindatemakhwo okhuba omuyeyi tawe?”"
  19,21,"Naboola mbu: “Ne endio nilwa kali, Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi aboolele mbu: 'Kano ni amangu muno khwisie, kho khumukhole eshimanyisio khubandu nende tsimbabaasi tsirulanga khwifwe. Ne lino ni likhuwa liamala okhubusibwa.'”"
  19,22,"Kho, nachinga inda yiyie, mana narula nayo okhutsia abundu ehale."
  19,23,"Mana obululu bwokhwibula nibumuyila hasi khushisina shiomutende, naboola mbu: “Emanyanga ndafwa kano nikashili okhunyoola, ndaba ndamala okhwibililwa khale.”"
  19,24,"Namulanga okhurulila hasi wuwe mbu: “Olabeelela tawe, toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi akhukholeele isebele hasi wuwo."
  19,25,"Ne resia ebuleka wuwo eshisina shiomutende; kwitsa okhukhulakasilia tsitende tsindayi, tsinyengu."
  19,26,"Kho, lia mana onywe, mana osangasie tsimoni. Ne nolola omundu yesiyesi, boola mbu: 'Toto esie elachile Omunji wetsimbabaasi okhwiyikalila okhusunga, kho inyanga yino shindalaboola nende Omundu yesiyesi tawe.'"""
  19,27,"Natsia ninaye khubandu bebe namuchinjile, nibaboola mbu: “Ewe Mariam, okholele likhuwa liamakana."
  19,28,"Ewe omukhana wabu Haruni, papa wuwo shiyali omundu omubii tawe ne mama wuwo yesi shiyali omuyeyi (omutamba) tawe.”"
  19,29,"Nabachomesilia olwala khuye (omwana oyo), nibaboola mbu: “Khwakhalomaloma khurie nende Omwana ushili indaana, omutoro ushilelungwa?”"
  19,30,"Naboola mbu: “Toto esie endi Omusumba wa Nyasaye. Yambelesiye Eshitabu, ne yakholele okhuba Omurumwa."
  19,31,"Ne yakholele okhuba weyikhabi wosiwosi wendi, ne yalachilisie okhulaama (Iswala) nende okhuyinia eshihanwa shia Izaka olwemba neshili omulamu."
  19,32,"Nende okhukholela mama wanje amalayi. Ne shiyakholele okhuba omufuru, omubii tawe."
  19,33,"Ne omulembe kube ninasi inyanga yandebulwa nende inyanga yandilifwa, nende inyanga yandililamusibwa okhuba omulamu.”"
  19,34,"Oyo niye Isa Omwana wa Mariam. Likhuwa liatoto eliabakanakanangamwo."
  19,35,"Shikakhoyeshele khu Nyasaye okhuba nende Omwana tawe. Obutswenufu nobubwe, niyenya eshindu aboolanga butswa mbu: “Ba!” Ni shiba."
  19,36,"“Ne toto Nyasaye ni Omulesi wanje nende Omulesi wenyu. Kho, mumulaame. Ino niyo injila ilunjifu.”"
  19,37,"Halali emikanda chiakabukhana abeene khu beene. Kho mana eshinyasio eshikhongo shilinyoola balia abakhaya, khulwa okhuula khwe inyanga ikhongo eyo."
  19,38,"Baliwulila ne balilola obulayi buli burie inyanga yabalikhwitsila? Halali abakhayi lelo bali mubukori obwa habulafu."
  19,39,"Ne obekanyilisie inyanga yokhwiyitsulisia ebise bielikhuwa lilibusibwa, nabo bali mukhukoyana nemana shibasubilanga tawe."
  19,40,"Ne toto ni efwe khulichelama eshialo nende bioosi bili hekulu washio. Ne balikalusibwa khwifwe."
  19,41,"Ne rumbula mushitabu shino Ibrahim, toto ye yali owatoto muno, Omurumwa."
  19,42,"Olwa yaboolela Samwana mbu: “Ewe papa wanje, shina shichilanga nolaama ebilawulila nende ebilalola, nende ebilakhukhoonya shiosishiosi tawe?"
  19,43,"Ewe papa wanje, toto bwene enyoolele obumanyi bushili okhukhulilakhwo ewe. Kho nonda, nditsa okhulunjisia khu injila ya habwene."
  19,44,"Ewe papa wanje, olalaama Shetani tawe. Toto Shetani yaloba (amakhuwa ka Nyasaye) Omunji wetsimbabaasi."
  19,45,"Ewe papa wanje, toto eritsanga eshinyasio shirulanga khuwetsimbabaasi okhukhunyoola. Ne olaba alala nende Shetani.”"
  19,46,"Naboola mbu: “Koo, shiwenya Abanyasaye banje tawe ewe Ibrahim? Nolalekha (akoboolanga ako) tawe, toto ndalakhulasa amachina. Ne ndulakhwo otsie ehale mbelio.”"
  19,47,"Naboola mbu: “Omulembe kube ninawe. Nditsa okhusabila Nyasaye wanje Omulesi eshileshelo. Toto Ye yambulilanga muno."
  19,48,"Nasi nditsa okhubarulakhwo, nende akamulaamanga akalali aka Nyasaye ako. Ne nditsa okhusaba Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ne shinditsa okhuba ukhola obubii nesaba Nyasaye wanje omulesi tawe.”"
  19,49,"Kho olwa yalekhana nabo nende kalia akabalaamanga akalali ka Nyasaye tawe, khwamuhelesia Is’haka nende Yaqub, ne buli shiamulala nikhumukhola okhuba Omurumwa."
  19,50,"Ne nikhubahelesia tsimbabaasi tsiefu, ne nikhubakhola okhuba nende olulimi lwatoto olwa hekulu."
  19,51,"Ne rumbula mushitabu shino Musa. Toto ye yali Omutswenufu Omwaule, ne yali Omurumwa, Omunabii."
  19,52,"Olwa khwamulanga ebuleka womukhono omusatsa weshikulu, mana nikhumusitia ahambi okhuboola ninafu mubwifisi."
  19,53,"Ne khutsimbabaasi tsiefu, nikhumuhelesia omusiani wabu mbu Haruni yesi abe Omunabii."
  19,54,"Ne rumbula mushitabu shino Ismail. Toto ye yali owatoto khubulakani, ne yali Omurumwa, Omunabii."
  19,55,"Ne yalomesinjia Abandu bebe iswala (okhulaama) nende izakaa (eshihanwa), ne yali yachamilwa ewa Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi."
  19,56,"Ne rumbula mushitabo shino Idris. Toto ye yali owa obwatoto muno, Omurumwa."
  19,57,"Mana nikhumuchingula habundu hekulu muno."
  19,58,"Abo nibo aba Nyasaye yahelesia omukabo mubarumwa mulwibulo lwa Adam, nende balia abakhwabachinga halala nende Nuhu, nende olwibulo lwa Ibrahim nende Israil, nende balia abakhwalunjisia mana nikhubaawula. Nibasomelwa tsinyali tsia Owetsimbabaasi, bakwitsanga nibasujuda nibalila."
  19,59,"Halali nibabalondakhwo inyuma wabu abaloondi ababii, nibarenguya okhulaama (Iswala) mana nibaloonda obwikombi obubii, kho balinyoolana nende eshinyasio eshululu."
  19,60,"Halali balia abekanila mana nibasuubila, ne nibakhola amakhuwa amalayi, abo balinjila mumukunda kwomwikulu, ne shibalikholelwakhwo obubii bwosibwosi tawe."
  19,61,"Mumikunda chiomwikulu chilaliwa tawe, echia Owetsimbabaasi yalaka Abasumba bebe mubwifisi. Ye toto indache yiyie buli lwoosi yulangasa."
  19,62,"Shibaliwulilamwo amakhuwa kabula obukhala tawe halali omulembesa, ne balinyoolamwo omukabo kwabu itsuli nende ingolobe."
  19,63,"Oko nikwo omukunda kwomwikulu, okwa khulichelemia Abasumba befu balia abaali nibaria Nyasaye."
  19,64,"Ne shikhwikhanga tawe halali khubunyali bwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi. Neebibie ebili imbeli wefu nende inyuma wefu, nende ebili hakari hao. Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi shini wokhwibilila tawe."
  19,65,"Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo, nende ebili hakari wabio; kho mulaame Ye butswa, ne wisumilisie mukhumulama. Koo, wamanyakhwo yesiyesi uli shinga Ye?"
  19,66,"Ne Omundu aboolanga mbu: “Koo, olwandiliba nefwile, toto ndililamusibwa ndaba omulamu?”"
  19,67,"Koo, Omundu shiyetsulilanga mbu toto khwamuloonga inyuma hawo naye nalali eshindu tawe?"
  19,68,"Kho, nditsuba khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi mbu toto khulibakhung’asia abo halala nende amashetani, mana khulibara mumbeka mwomulilo kwa Jahanam nibasikame."
  19,69,"Mana toto khulirusia buli mumukanda balia mubo abaloba muno Nyasaye Owetsimbabaasi."
  19,70,"Ne toto efwe khwamanya muno abakhoyeshele okhusambwamwo."
  19,71,"Ne abulao yesiyesi mwinywe halali alikuulakhwo (khu Jahanam). Elo nilikhuwa lili khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi eliamala okhubusibwa."
  19,72,"Mana khulihabina balia bamuria, ne khulilekhamwo ababii nibasikame."
  19,73,"Ne nibasomelwa tsinyali tsiefu tsili habulafu, abakhayi baboolelanga abasuubili mbu: “Ni mukanda shina khuchibili chino kuli nende eshimenyo eshilayi nende Abandu boluyali?”"
  19,74,"Ne emikanda chinga chiakhwasishia imbeli wabu khumika chiabura, chiali nende amarone amalayi muno nende habundu alayi muno?"
  19,75,"Boola mbu: “Balia bali mubukori, lekhe Owetsimbabaasi abametele ebise okhula balole akabalakungwa, eshinyasio nohomba Indukho. Awo nawabalimanya mbu niwina weshimenyo eshibii nende owa abalwaani abateshele muno.”"
  19,76,"Ne Nyasaye ametelanga obulunjifu balia abalunjikha. Ne ebikhole ebilayi bitong’anga, neebilayi muno khumurungo ewa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, ne naamakalusio amalayi."
  19,77,"Koo, walolakhwo ulia owakhaya ebimanyisio biefu mana naboola mbu: “Toto esie nditsa okhuhebwa omwandu nende Abana?”"
  19,78,"Koo, ye yanyola amakhuwa kefisa, nohomba Owetsimbabaasi yamulaka?"
  19,79,"Shikali kario tawe. Khwitsa okhuhandika akaboolanga, ne khulamumeta muno ebise bieshinyasio."
  19,80,"Ne khulimuhelesia akaboolanga ako, ne alikhwitsila nali yenyene."
  19,81,"Ne bekholela abanyasaye baandi habundu wa Nyasaye mbu khobanyoole amaani (oluyali)."
  19,82,"Shikali kario tawe. Balikongola okhulamwa khwabu okho, ne baliba abasuku babu."
  19,83,"Koo, shimulolangakhwo mbu efwe khwaruma amashetani khubakhayi, ababaretsangamwo amaani kokhukhola amabii?"
  19,84,"Kho olabayuyukhanila tawe. Efwe toto khubabalilanga tsinyanga tsiabu."
  19,85,"Inyanga yakhulikhung’asia abaria Nyasaye okhubayila khuwetsimbabaasi babe abacheni be."
  19,86,"Ne khulichomia ababii mumulilo kwa Jahannam, nibali nende omwalakho omunji."
  19,87,"Shibaliba nende obunyali bwokhusabila abandi eshileshelo tawe, halali balia bakhola indakano ewa Omunji wetsimbabaasi."
  19,88,"Ne baboola mbu: “Omunji wetsimbabaasi yekholela Omwana.”"
  19,89,"Toto mwarera likhuwa liokhusinya muno."
  19,90,"Likulu lili hambi muno okhwatikha, ne liloba okhwarukha, ne tsingulu okhukwa ebitonyetonye."
  19,91,"Khulwa bachikha mbu Omunji wetsimbabaasi yekholela Omwana."
  19,92,"Ne shikakhoyeshela Omunji Wetsimbabaasi okhwikholela Omwana tawe."
  19,93,"Abulaho yesiyesi khubali mwikulu nende mushialo halali alitsila Omunji wetsimbabaasi nali Omusumba."
  19,94,"Ne toto yamala okhubamanya, ne yababala obulayi muno."
  19,95,"Ne buli shiamulala alimwitsila Ye (Nyasaye) inyanga yeyindukho yenyene."
  19,96,"Netoto balia basuubila mana nibakhola amalayi Omunji wetsimbabaasi alibakholela obuyanzi."
  19,97,"Ne toto khwakhuanguyilia (Ikurani) khulusungo lulwo kho obiile akomwikhoyo khuyo balia abaria Nyasaye, ne wikanyilisie khuyo Abandu bayingananga muno."
  19,98,"Ne emikanda chinga echia khwasishia imbeli wabu? Ololangakhwo mulala khubo nohomba obawulilangakho nibemonyelesia?"
